al, and aligned with the site theme. Do not invent legal text that pretends to be final counsel-approved policy. Use clear placeholder copy where final legal language is required. Investor Relations should be a credible pathway page, not fake financial information. NDA page should explain how NDA requests will be handled later, not generate real legal documents. Use refined typography, structured sections, simple graphics, and CTA to contact. Run lint/build.\"\n265 |   },\n266 |   {\n267 |     \"id\": \"33-mobile-responsive-pass\",\n268 |     \"title\": \"Mobile responsive polish across all pages\",\n269 |     \"scope\": \"responsive-qa\",\n270 |     \"target\": \"all public pages\",\n271 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": true,\n272 |     \"prompt\": \"Perform a mobile responsive polish pass across landing and all public pages. Do not redesign. Fix only layout issues. Check hero, Quick Search, all homepage sections, Why GFF AI, Capabilities, Industries, Platforms, Build, Resources, Company, Contact, Portal, Client, Legal pages. Ensure no horizontal overflow, good section spacing, readable text, tappable buttons, stacked cards, simplified timelines, usable forms, scrollable tabs where needed, and architecture diagrams that adapt to mobile. Preserve approved landing visual design and hero video placement. Do not add new features. Run lint/build.\"\n273 |   },\n274 |   {\n275 |     \"id\": \"34-accessibility-and-motion-pass\",\n276 |     \"title\": \"Accessibility and motion quality pass\",\n277 |     \"scope\": \"accessibility-qa\",\n278 |     \"target\": \"all public pages\",\n279 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": true,\n280 |     \"prompt\": \"Perform accessibility and motion quality pass. Do not redesign. Ensure each public page has one clear H1, semantic sections, accessible links/buttons, visible focus states, form labels, keyboard-friendly interactions, no clickable divs without keyboard behavior, readable contrast, and prefers-reduced-motion support for animations. C