25) + (Data\\\\_Readiness \\\\times 0.20) + (Process\\\\_Complexity \\\\times 0.20) + (Transformation\\\\_Readiness \\\\times 0.15)$$\\n  - However, in `components/sections/BuildAIEnterpriseSection.tsx` (lines 135-141), the scores passed to the formula are currently hardcoded for simulation:\\n    ```typescript\\n    const score = calculateBlueprintScore({\\n      aiMaturityScore: 60,\\n      businessNeedScore: 80,\\n      dataReadinessScore: 50,\\n      processComplexityScore: 50,\\n      transformationReadinessScore: 80\\n    });\\n    ```\\n    This results in a static score of **64** for any answers provided by the user.\\n  - The required Banking test case (**Banking, 15000 employees, Scaling AI, Productivity + Cost Reduction + Compliance, Mostly Integrated Data, Budget Approved**) does not map to dynamic inputs and thus does not return **87/100**.\\n  - **Resolution Need**: In future tasks, we need to map user selections to dynamic maturity values and ensure the specified banking test case evaluates exactly to **87**.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Design System Observations\\n* Refined, premium visual styling (dark `#010101` and `#000613` backgrounds, glassmorphism card design, glowing color maps).\\n* Seamless custom SVG iconography, premium gradients (`#E4000F` to `#009DFF`), and balanced responsive layouts.\\n* Clean visual hierarchy adhering strictly to the Apple-like \\\"Apple 2026 Enterprise AI\\\" standard, without excessive badging or generic robot imagery.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Validation Baseline\\n* **Linting**: Passed successfully.\\n* **Static compilation (`npm run build`)**: Compiled successfully in `6.0s` with zero errors.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Recommended Next Task\\n* **Task ID**: `01-safety-cleanup-no-slug-no-publicroutepage` to ensure that any potential routing folders or leftover catch-all directories are completely cleared from the project and that the base explicit App Router folders are clean before adding explicit files. Or proceed immediately to scoring logic alignment under task `10-verify-and-fix-blueprint-generator-scoring`.\"}}\n./automation/logs/2026-06-25T22-42-26-390Z-00-preflight-project-context-implement.log:208:{\"ts\":\"2026-06-25T22:42:25.930Z\",\"type\":\"agent_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_end\",\"contentType\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I have completed the preflight project context and guardrail audit. Here is the comprehensive report as requested:\\n\\n### Files Inspected\\n1. `package.json` — Checked dependencies, framework versions, scripts, and styling dependencies.\\n2. `tsconfig.json` — Verified compiler options and paths aliases.\\n3. `app/page.tsx` — Inspected root App Router configuration and landing page linkage.\\n4. `components/LandingPage.tsx` — Audited structure of homepage and included sections.\\n5. `components/Header.tsx` & `components/Footer.tsx` — Inspected existing navigation items and links.\\n6. `components/sections/` (All files) — Audited individual section components for design and rendering completeness.\\n7. `lib/landing-data.ts` — Verified lists, steps, and static cards.\\n8. `lib/blueprint-data.ts` — Audited scoring formulas, types, fields, and options.\\n9. `lib/nav-data.ts` & `lib/site-config.ts` — Verified site-wide metadata and path definitions.\\n10. `components/sections/BuildAIEnterpriseSection.tsx` — Inspected the interactive blueprint generator section.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Audit Findings\\n\\n#### 1. Framework, Routing Model & Styling Stack\\n* **Framework**: Next.js `16.2.9` with React `19.2.4`.\\n* **Routing Model**: Next.js App Router.\\n* **Styling Stack**: Tailwind CSS (version `4.x.x` via `@tailwindcss/postcss`) with variables defined in `app/globals.css`.\\n\\n#### 2. Animation & UI Libraries Availability\\n* **Animation Library**: `motion/react` (version `12.40.0`) is installed and used extensively. The legacy `framer-motion` package is **not** installed.\\n* **Aceternity UI Components**: Only `components/ui/world-map.tsx` and `components/ui/3d_view.tsx` are